data.description: Gorgeous home in the Magnolias of Brook Highland! This lovely 4 Bedroom All-Brick home is ready for new owners. You'll love the main level living with formal living room, family room, eat-in Kitchen, and dining room. Upstairs is the large private Master Suite as well as three well-appointed guest rooms with another full bathroom. Need more room...check out the finished basement space with playroom, office space and another full bathroom. Enjoy the large, flat backyard: perfect for playtime and cookouts. This home is convenient to 280 and all that it has to offer: close to restaurants, shopping and hospitals. WELCOME HOME!! ASK ABOUT ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE OPTION! Seller is offering a $5,000 allowance for upgrades!
